 ma0d xc h28 y204 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE first thought in the minds of many, on </div><div class="t m39f x64 h28 y91f ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">learning that in the first covenant the people made </div><div class="t m98a x64 h28 y32b ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a promise which they could not possibly fulfill, is </div><div class="t ma0e x64 h28 y35 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that God was unjust to require such a promise. </div><div class="t m596 x64 h28 y395 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">And since they know that God is not unjust, they </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
